{"tid":342381,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(畫畫) 有關運用arcylic一問","createTime":"2017-07-31T14:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T04:48:12.000Z","uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d45eb090cfe60e30b3b0777ed8007a196edecb6","tid":342381,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"小弟通常畫畫都係用arcylic, 但係問題就嚟la, 如果想畫出嚟d色係乾淨嘅(d 色好混俗同啞) 有冇咩方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc15125385e0ee1fb92611d5b28ca453d060442d","tid":342381,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d766ccce86f9d8f0337db38993938613d878c212","tid":342381,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca6db940b2cf61cba2f1a781a4ce069470534889","tid":342381,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af308b33771797e3f3f7f2416e6ab7897fe55a0b","tid":342381,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb55557bca5b9cd9dd781cafe342c321a6d64347","tid":342381,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435f759b06be4439ace339cdd504b6649be36fcb","tid":342381,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6a6968a605e5f7add95e0c6abe753c4a69e33fd7","tid":342381,"uid":131630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟通常畫畫都係用arcylic, 但係問題就嚟la, 如果想畫出嚟d色係乾淨嘅(d 色好混俗同啞) 有冇咩方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我未用過acrylic 多數用電繪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都比比見意啦<br />\n我家姐收art 日日都用acrylic<br />\n唔想啲色咁混俗可以等層顏料乾左先再上第二層tone<br />\n每層都唔好太厚<br />\n覺得晒時間就可以用風筒吹乾佢<br />\n希望可以幫到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0971d53f640cc768ad35787c2baff6053aeb9c1b","tid":342381,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:31:35.000Z","msg":"顏料都不外乎<br />\n<br />\n厚塗（淨顏料）<br />\n薄塗（稀釋）<br />\n溝色（淨顏料/稀釋）<br />\n上完一層，乾透再上其他<br />\n上完一層，未乾再上其他<br />\n<br />\n自己試到啱比例同方法先落筆"},{"pid":"5be2ca62b3cf636d596d5e44be1af4ff06572c94","tid":342381,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:34:15.000Z","msg":"溝完色或用完一隻色，記得洗筆，再重複以上方法，因為有啲色溝埋就污糟。"},{"pid":"c6e8f393570c7d256d8eb7b2b738c25b3f06f546","tid":342381,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溝完色或用完一隻色，記得洗筆，再重複以上方法，因為有啲色溝埋就污糟。</blockquote><br />\n通常會準備兩兜水，一兜乾淨溝色用，一兜洗筆用，洗筆水有機會常換。"},{"pid":"2a2c80aa2a5d38a9c8bf8112e2f7fe40453b17e7","tid":342381,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>顏料都不外乎<br />\n<br />\n厚塗（淨顏料）<br />\n薄塗（稀釋）<br />\n溝色（淨顏料/稀釋）<br />\n上完一層，乾透再上其他<br />\n上完一層，未乾再上其他<br />\n<br />\n自己試到啱比例同方法先落筆</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,thx"},{"pid":"3bf6c2495a63ac3febac79a45e245c6cb042c81b","tid":342381,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟通常畫畫都係用arcylic, 但係問題就嚟la, 如果想畫出嚟d色係乾淨嘅(d 色好混俗同啞) 有冇咩方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我未用過acrylic 多數用電繪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都比比見意啦<br />\n我家姐收art 日日都用acrylic<br />\n唔想啲色咁混俗可以等層顏料乾左先再上第二層tone<br />\n每層都唔好太厚<br />\n覺得晒時間就可以用風筒吹乾佢<br />\n希望可以幫到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,thx"}]}